  <md:title>Weighted Means</md:title>
  <md:abstract>An introduction to weighted means intended for an elementary/intermediate algebra course.  Includes examples related to calculating grades and GPA.</md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>edce6a8e-e982-4b4d-a884-8b53a6d08b88</md:uuid>
